---
description: The brand collection contains raw hex codes and font variables.  Nothing in this collection implies intent, role, UI usage or component usage.

globs: src/components/**/*.tsx

alwaysApply: false
---

## Color Rules:

All colors are stored as pure hex values. Colors have no semantic meaning. Colors are grouped by hue.

---

## Scale Structure:

Scales use a 100-1200 scale. Lower number is lighter and higher numbers are darker. 
Allowed Increments:
100 by default
50 when intermediate values are needed.
25 when further refinement is also needed.

---

## Font Styles & Weights:
Font styles and font weights are included as string variables.

---

## Other Instructions:
White and black are in their own group called “Foundations”.
